parent1.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with radiant feathers in the style of abstract expressionism. It perches on the edge of a craggy cliff overlooking a vast desert under a twilight sky, casting a warm glow from its wings, amidst a landscape of wind-carved rock formations and floating glass orbs.

parent2.code: A detailed watercolor of a radiant golden phoenix with fiery flaming feathers in the style of surrealism. It is majestically soaring above the crumbling rooftops in an ancient, mystical city on a stormy, overcast day, gracefully scattering glowing embers from its ethereal wings, amidst an environment of twisting, towering spires and shimmering, floating lanterns.

offspring.code: A sketch of a golden phoenix with shimmering wings in the style of cubism. It stands atop the frost-covered peak in an otherworldly landscape during a clear night, casting a cold, luminescent glow from its body amidst a scene of crystalline ice sculptures and floating luminous auroras.
